{"tid":267253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋8日內兩工傷 工人遭磨機割傷右腳","createTime":"2017-06-02T06:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T07:24:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5da3676018ddeaeceadcd3c6ca3cc1232eeb776f","tid":267253,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"大嶼山港珠澳大橋人工島地盤，繼8日前發生工人高處墮下意外後，今日再爆工傷。早上10時許，一名工人工作期間，疑遭大型磨機割傷右腳，工友報警。傷者在現場經包紮後，被送往北大嶼山醫院治理，當局正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n上周四，香港口岸人工島B1區，一名35歲姓黃工人在電梯槽內墮下受傷，送往瑪嘉烈醫院，情況一度危殆。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56773010&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56773010%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170602&d=i9aJShi6wDRnb7T0HJaU7iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1019a90f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56773010%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170602&h=5910aa09\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56773010&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170602</a>"},{"pid":"8c4409fcb536106102f86629795c19143a46ce5a","tid":267253,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"咁多工傷 個盤可以繼續開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e806093d6dde90f1e98fd8933ba485365f00d4c","tid":267253,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"目測工人右腳無事 怕就合埋眼做野"},{"pid":"13bd1c7bf343d06e28107103a5a9ef54dbf6c15b","tid":267253,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多工傷 個盤可以繼續開工<img 